            <h2>Details</h2>
            <p>The Run For Love 5K is an annual event to help raise money to fight substance use and addiction.</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Held rain or shine</li>
              <li>Walk or run - feel free to go at your own pace</li>
              <li>Dogs are welcome</li>
              <li>There will be a raffle booth and tickets sold at the event</li>
              <li>Water will be provided at the start and finish, and at the halfway point.</li>
              <li>Option to be timed with prizes for 1st, 2nd, and 3rd.</li>
            </ul>
